text: Tanja Žutić (29 January 1927 - 11 January 2005) was a Slovenian gymnast. She competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:2005 deaths Category:Slovenian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Ptuj
